	Riding a train to class is the most comfortable, fastest , reliable and
fun way. No worry to the traffic! Train will stop only at station or halt,
so it will be easier to predict the arrive time more than the other vehicle.
The more accurate, the less time to spend.

	This project was accquired an idea from the developer.
Going the the work or class and back to home by a train almost everyday. 
Thus, waiting a train with hopeless is time burning! Knowing a lastest train
status will gain : lastest time at lastest arrive station and this will be
less time-consuming for waiting a train. 